# mercure

A bot for the Google AI challenge 2010 (http://ai-contest.com/)

## Usage

The bot needs to be run with a game controller respecting the
specification on http://ai-contest.com/specification.php 
The official engine and a game replay viewer are in the tools/
directory. The match.sh file is a convenience script that runs a match
and pipes the output to the replay viewer. 

Syntax: match.sh path/to/bot_jar_or_bin path/to/bot2

## Installation and compilation

You need leiningen: http://github.com/technomancy/leiningen
At the project root:
lein deps # will downloads dependencies
lein uberjar # will compile the project jar with all runtime deps inside

